::DrillBit::

He wakes up as he hears DarkMouse's message.
"uhh... yeah, sure."
He opens a comm to Dollen.
"Dollen, go stay with DarkMouse. Some bots are after her."
He then opens a comm to the Energonians.
"This is Commander DrillBit. Dark Mouse has no wish to switch alliances
at this time. Please to not make us use force to protect her. Just
leave. If you attempt to kid nap her, we will protect her with lethal
force."

::Dollen::

"Sure, Commander." 
He walks to the mess hall, and sits with Dark Mouse.
"DrillBit is talking with them."
